 extent do you agree or disagree?","question_type":"agree_disagree","taskType":"task2"},{"slug":"unhealthy-foods-taxation","title":"Unhealthy Foods and Taxation","prompt":"Some think that governments should tax unhealthy foods to encourage people to eat healthier. To what extent do you agree or disagree?","question_type":"agree_disagree","taskType":"task2"},{"slug":"zoos-and-rare-animals","title":"Zoos and Rare Animals","prompt":"Many people think that zoos are cruel. Others think they are helpful in protecting rare animals. Discuss both sides and give your own opinion.","question_type":"discuss_both_views","taskType":"task2"},{"slug":"roads-in-major-cities","title":"Roads in Major Cities","prompt":"The roads in major cities today are often difficult to travel on. What are the causes of this? What are some possible solutions?","question_type":"causes_solutions","taskType":"task2"},{"slug":"shopping-malls-public-parks","title":"Shopping Malls vs Public Parks","prompt":"Some people think that it is better to build more public parks and sports facilities in new towns rather than shopping malls. To what extent do you agree or disagree?","question_type":"agree_disagree","taskType":"task2"},{"slug":"academic-practical-education","title":"Academic vs Practical Education","prompt":"Students should be primarily taught academic subjects so that they can pass exams, and practical skills such as cooking should not be taught. To what extent do you agree or disagree?","question_type":"agree_disagree","taskType":"task2"},{"slug":"ambition-characteristic","title":"Ambition as a Characteristic","prompt":"Some think that ambition is a good quality. Is it important to be ambitious? Is it a positive or negative characteristic?","question_type":"positive_negative","taskType":"task2"},{"slug":"choosing-career-early","title":"Choosing Career Early","prompt":"The job market today is very competitive and it is best to choose a career or field of study early in order to get a good job later 